ommand or your ftp client.','Cannot update .htaccess'=>'Cannot update .htaccess','WP Super Cache has checked the front page of your blog. Please visit %s if you would like to disable this.'=>'WP Super Cache has checked the front page of your blog. Please visit %s if you would like to disable this.','[%s] Front page check!'=>'[%s] Front page check!','The cache on your blog has been cleared because the front page of your site is missing the text "%2$s". Please visit %1$s to verify the cache has been cleared.'=>'The cache on your blog has been cleared because the front page of your site is missing the text "%2$s". Please visit %1$s to verify the cache has been cleared.','[%s] Front page is not correct! Cache Cleared!'=>'[%s] Front page is not correct! Cache Cleared!','Please visit %1$s to clear the cache as the front page of your site is not correct and missing the text, "%2$s"!'=>'Please visit %1$s to clear the cache as the front page of your site is not correct and missing the text, "%2$s"!','[%s] Front page is not correct! Please clear cache!'=>'[%s] Front page is not correct! Please clear cache!','The cache on your blog has been cleared because the front page of your site is now downloading. Please visit %s to verify the cache has been cleared.'=>'The cache on your blog has been cleared because the front page of your site is now downloading. Please visit %s to verify the cache has been cleared.','[%s] Front page is gzipped! Cache Cleared!'=>'[%s] Front page is gzipped! Cache Cleared!','Please visit %s to clear the cache as the front page of your site is now downloading!'=>'Please visit %s to clear the cache as the front page of your site is now downloading!','[%s] Front page is gzipped! Please clear cache!'=>'[%s] Front page is gzipped! Please clear cache!','Warning! WP Super Cache caching <strong>was</strong> broken but has been <strong>fixed</strong>! The script advanced-cache.php could not load wp-cache-phase1.php.<br /><br />The file %1$s/advanced-cache.php has